data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  Don't wait another second to come check out this beautiful home located in the Silver Canyon Subdivision! This lovely home not only has a large sized backyard but also a roomy covered patio making it perfect for entertaining, which is amplified inside with a spacious downstairs featuring the Living Room, spacious Kitchen and Dining Area. Upstairs you will find a is a second living space perfect for an office, study or play area for the kiddos, the very roomy primary bedroom and bathroom with a wonderful walk-in shower and double vanity sink.
